title: Labyrinth Holistic Cafe
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, International, Organic, Western, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Offers vegan choices and others possibly can be made vegan, so please inquire. All cakes, pastas & sauces are gluten free. The staff are fully trained in all aspects of dietary requirements and the kitchen operates under strict anti cross contamination conditions. Main menu is made-in-house from scratch & to order. Does not use wheat flour and all desserts are gluten free and a few are vegan too.
